ed="T" n="0727b05"/><persName key="A001414">釋圓測</persName>者，未詳氏族也<ptr target="#n787"/>。自幼明敏，慧解縱<lb
ed="T" n="0727b06"/>橫。<persName key="A000294">三藏奘師</persName>為<placeName key="PL000000042410">慈恩</placeName><persName key="A001019">基師</persName>講新翻《唯識論》<ptr target="#n767"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0727b07"/><persName key="A001414">測</persName>賂守門者隱聽，歸則緝綴<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g542"/>義章。將欲罷<lb
ed="T" n="0727b08"/>講，<persName key="A001414">測</persName>於<placeName key="PL000000042216">西明寺</placeName>鳴鐘召眾，稱講《唯識》。<persName key="A001019">基</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0727b09"/>慊<ptr type="glossary" target="#g543"/>其有奪人之心，遂讓<persName key="A001414">測</persName>講訓。<persName key="A000294">奘</persName>講《瑜伽》，<lb
ed="T" n="0727b10"/>還同前盜聽受之，而亦不後<persName key="A001019">基</persName>也。<anchor xml:id="beg0727sgsz2"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>詒</sic><corr>迨</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0727sgsz2"/><date notBefore-iso="+0679-06-17" key="j19692271973032" notAfter-iso="+0689-11-16"><persName key="A002146">高宗</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0727b11"/>之末，<persName key="A002099">天后</persName>之初</date>，應義解<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g544"/>之選，入譯經館，眾<lb
ed="T" n="0727b12"/>皆推挹。及翻《大乘顯識》<ptr target="#n98"/>等經，<persName key="A001414">測</persName>充證義<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g54"/>，與<lb
ed="T" n="0727b13"/><persName key="A008985">薄塵</persName>、<persName key="A008979">靈辯</persName>、<persName key="A008981">嘉尚</persName>攸<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g545"/>方其駕。所著《唯識疏鈔》，<lb
ed="T" n="0727b14"/>詳解經論，天下分行焉。</p>
